73
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:48,360
Mobil itu

74
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,360
Apa?

75
00:05:50,360 --> 00:05:51,960
Apa aku terlambat?

76
00:05:51,960 --> 00:05:53,960
Hai, Chiba, tunggu!

77
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,060
Numpang lewat!

78
