124
00:08:11,060 --> 00:08:12,460
Kakakmu?

125
00:08:12,460 --> 00:08:15,960
Karashima adalah pengemudinya.

126
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,960
Mio.

127
00:08:18,160 --> 00:08:20,060
Pengemudi yang tewas itu

128
00:08:20,060 --> 00:08:21,260
