230
00:13:16,441 --> 00:13:17,741
Ayah?

231
00:13:17,741 --> 00:13:20,641
Tuan Mouri! Jangan-jangan...

232
00:13:20,641 --> 00:13:22,041
Petugas Takagi,

233
00:13:22,041 --> 00:13:24,241
